HOW TO RUN HYPHY:
1. if using a subset of genes, copy them into a new directory
2. run 0110_run_aln_filter.sh / aln_filter.py to make the output directory with -100-100 
3. make genetrees for hyphy input in 03_run_iqtree_script.sh
4. then can run the hyphy generation scripts in 00_run_hyphyGen.sh with the 100-100/nt
5. the 00_run_hyphyGen.sh script will make 


emily also has a much more detailed readme file at /ix1/nclark/ekopania/FOR_JUSTINE/HYPHY_SCRIPTS/README



